)

Constructor.

Parameters:
[in] server_host TCP access to DTrack2 server: hostname or IP address of ARTtrack Controller, empty string if not used
[in] server_port TCP access to DTrack2 server: port number of ARTtrack Controller, default 50105
[in] data_port UDP port number to receive tracking data from ARTtrack Controller (0 if to be chosen)
[in] data_bufsize size of buffer for UDP packets (in bytes)
[in] data_timeout_us UDP timeout (receiving) in us (in micro second)
[in] server_timeout_us TCP timeout for access to DTrack2 server (in micro second; receiving and sending)
